{"tid":584622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰鬥民族] 睇完紅雀特工, 今日即刻有條現實版新聞流出","createTime":"2018-03-08T03:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T03:09:14.000Z","uid":175119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fae84489e4eca2026b91a1a186d5bb2ba9a8d025","tid":584622,"uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/07/world/europe/russia-spy-nerve-agent.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-spy-nerve-agent.html&d=XBXBPRE%2Bj1Svc0DLDaslyYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=66869d1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/07/world/europe/russia-spy-nerve-agent.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2010年前俄羅斯情報員依照交換條件移居英國, 呢個禮拜同個女喺英國大型購物商場俾人用神經毒意圖殺害後獲救, 目前深切治療中未回復意識<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/110612_1c0c3553cb21b04415907f084aa37e71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F110612_1c0c3553cb21b04415907f084aa37e71.jpg&h=a3f3ba8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未睇套戲前會覺得單新聞無乜特別...睇完之後覺得好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}